comments: Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lillard (POR) and makes marginal contact during the pick that does not prevent him from disengaging.
LAR shows Westbrook (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Aminu (POR) and does not deliver contact as the two players briefly engage.
RLB shows Westbrook (OKC) briefly grasps Lillard (POR) during the pick but does not affect his SQBR.
George (OKC) makes marginal contact to Kanter's (POR) arm after he has secure the ball.

RAR shows Grant (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his SQBR.  Lillard initiates the contact and falls to the floor on his own.
[Observable in enhanced video] Lillard (POR) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Harkless (POR) makes contact to Westbrook's (OKC) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Kanter (POR) firms up in a screening position in the path of Westbrook (OKC) and does not deliver contact.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Lillard's (POR) arm during the drive to the basket that does not affect his SQBR.
Adams (OKC) briefly grabs and releases Kanter's (POR) arm during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Both Kanter (POR) and Lillard (POR) make incidental contact with Westbrook (OKC) that does not cause him to lose control of the ball.
RAR shows Harkless (POR) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball defending Westbrook (OKC).
George (OKC) places a hand/arm to the front of Harkless (POR) at the start of the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Lillard (POR) makes incidental contact with Adams (OKC) that does not affect his ability to secure the loose ball and pass.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Kanter's (POR) arm that does not affect his SQBR.
Westbrook (OKC) is in the lane without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Grant (OKC) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) and cleanly blocks his driving shot attempt.
Kanter (POR) gathers the ball with his right foot on the floor and legally takes two steps during his drive to the basket.
Adams (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Kanter (POR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lillard (POR) and delivers slight contact that Lillard is able to move through when they move along the same path.
Ferguson (OKC) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Grant (OKC) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) establishing post position.
Adams (OKC) briefly grasps Harkless' (POR) arm during the screen but releases without affecting his SQBR.
Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with Grant (OKC) that does not affect his dunk attempt.
George (OKC) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
